《城市：天际线》普遍獲得媒體的好評，根據評論匯總網站[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]的資料，遊戲的平均分數為86.49%<ref name="GR" />，而另一個網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根據60份評論給予遊戲85/100分<ref name="MCPC" />。

[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]的賈森·福克納（Jason Faulkner）給予本作9分（滿分10分），表示自己“十分享受游戏的每分每秒，并且对我的城市的规划、建造与培育带来了超远于本作标题所带给的想象力与创造力”，認為《城市：天际线》不只是回歸到城市建造類遊戲的初心，還更進一步擴展、完善它<ref name="Destructoid" />。[[IGN|IGN]]的丹·斯塔普萊頓（Dan Stapleton）给出8.5分（滿分10分），写到“不要期望有天灾和随机事件，但是可以期望城市建设者为你带来规模与各种设施运作的震撼”<ref name="ign_review" />。《[[The_Escapist|The Escapist]]》的喬納森·博爾丁（Jonathan Bolding）给出滿分5星，认为遊戲雖然有些小瑕疵，但仍然是“最近十年来一款最好的城市建造游戏”，喜歡經營模擬與城市建造的玩家都應該要體驗看看<ref name="Escapist_page1" /><ref name="Escapist_page2" />。《[[為戰而生|為戰而生]]》的總監兰迪·瓦内尔（Randy Varnell）表示這是他2015年最喜歡的遊戲之一，提到《城市：天际线》重新啟發了自己對城市建造遊戲的熱情<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2016/01/06/battleborn-39-s-randy-varnell-shares-his-games-of-the-year.aspx |title=Battleborn's Randy Varnell Shares His Top Games Of 2015 |author=GAME INFORMER STAFF |work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2016-01-06 |accessdate=2019-11-29 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129091951/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2016/01/06/battleborn-39-s-randy-varnell-shares-his-games-of-the-year.aspx |archivedate=2019-11-29 }}</ref>。

《[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]》的基斯杜化·里榮斯頓（Christopher Livingston）給《城市：天际线》86/100分，稱讚遊戲的用戶介面一目了然，搭配畫面上的「小啾啾」能夠馬上知道城市發生的問題；道路建設方面，建造道路很簡單，但要做出一條有意義的卻很難，玩家能夠從完善城市交通的過程中獲得樂趣，並總結到「遊戲雖然有些缺陷，但這款有趣且令人上癮的遊戲讓人趨之若鶩」<ref name="pcgamer review" />。[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]的編輯路克·彭凱特（Luke Plunkett）覺得能建設自己的城市很有趣，但管理起來卻很麻煩，市民會有許多問題等著解決，例如垃圾、汙水，最麻煩的莫過於塞車，即使是6線道，遊戲的AI也會讓他們擠在同一條<ref name="kotaku review">{{cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/cities-skylines-the-kotaku-review-1690432932 |title=Cities: Skylines: The Kotaku Review |first=Luke |last=Plunkett |website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |publisher={{link-en|Univision Communications}} |date=2015-03-10 |accessdate=2020-03-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327081040/https://kotaku.com/cities-skylines-the-kotaku-review-1690432932 |archivedate=2020-03-27 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。

[[模擬城市系列|模擬城市系列]]作为城市建造遊戲類型的標竿，《城市：天际线》不免被各家媒體、評論及玩家進行各種比較<ref name="Dean">{{cite web |url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-09-04-cities-skyline-is-out-to-satisfy-where-simcity-couldnt |title=Cities: Skyline is out to satisfy where SimCity couldn't |first=Paul |last=Dean |website=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |publisher=[[Gamer_Network|Gamer Network]] |date=2014-09-14 |accessdate=2020-03-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316065912/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-09-04-cities-skyline-is-out-to-satisfy-where-simcity-couldnt |archivedate=2020-03-16 }}</ref><ref name="greenlit" /><ref name="pcinvasion">{{Cite news |url=http://www.pcinvasion.com/cities-skylines-announced-at-paradox-fan-event |title=Cities: Skylines announced at Paradox fan event |date=2014-08-14 |work=PC Invasion |first=Peter |last=Parrish |accessdate=2020-03-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316070104/https://www.pcinvasion.com/cities-skylines-announced-at-paradox-fan-event/ |archivedate=2020-03-16 }}</ref>。但隨著2013年發售的《[[模拟城市_(2013年游戏)|模拟城市]]》因強制連線和遊戲機制的問題惹得玩家不滿，《城市：天际线》的推出被視為有力競爭者，甚至達到《模擬城市》難以超越的程度<ref name="Dean" /><ref name="greenlit" /><ref name="pcinvasion" />。遊戲推出以來，《城市：天际线》憑藉著低廉價格、優秀的遊戲AI、允許離線遊玩及更廣闊的遊戲地圖等優點獲得玩家喜愛<ref>{{cite web |last=Young |first=Shamus |title=SimCity vs. Cities: Skylines - Who Wins? |page=1 |url=https://v1.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/columns/experienced-points/13674-Comparing-SimCity-to-Cities-Skylines-Provides-an-Obvious-Winner |work=[[The_Escapist|The Escapist]] |date=2015-03-24 |accessdate=2020-03-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316072153/https://v1.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/columns/experienced-points/13674-Comparing-SimCity-to-Cities-Skylines-Provides-an-Obvious-Winner |archivedate=2020-03-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Young |first=Shamus |title=SimCity vs. Cities: Skylines - Who Wins? |page=2 |url=https://v1.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/columns/experienced-points/13674-Comparing-SimCity-to-Cities-Skylines-Provides-an-Obvious-Winner.2 |work=[[The_Escapist|The Escapist]] |date=2015-03-24 |accessdate=2020-03-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316072438/https://v1.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/video-games/columns/experienced-points/13674-Comparing-SimCity-to-Cities-Skylines-Provides-an-Obvious-Winner.2 |archivedate=2020-03-16 }}</ref>。評論普遍認為《城市：天际线》已經成功取代模拟城市系列，成為新的城市建造遊戲標竿<ref name="Dean" /><ref>{{cite web |last=Dingman |first=Hayden |title=Cities: Skylines is more like SimCity than SimCity |url=https://www.pcworld.com/article/2860755/cities-skylines-is-more-like-simcity-than-simcity.html |website=[[PC_World|PC World]] |date=2014-12-17 |accessdate=2015-04-20 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316072554/https://www.pcworld.com/article/2860755/cities-skylines-is-more-like-simcity-than-simcity.html |archivedate=2020-03-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Maiberg |first=Emanuel |title=The 'SimCity' Empire Has Fallen and 'Skylines' Is Picking Up the Pieces |url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/pgav4v/maxis-is-dead-but-this-game-is-better-than-simcity |work=Motherboard |publisher=[[Vice新聞|Vice]] |date=2015-03-17 |accessdate=2020-03-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316072729/https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/pgav4v/maxis-is-dead-but-this-game-is-better-than-simcity |archivedate=2020-03-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Tassi |first=Paul |title='Cities: Skylines' Succeeds Where EA's 'SimCity' Failed |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2015/03/14/cities-skylines-succeeds-where-eas-simcity-failed/ |date=2015-03-14 |website=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |accessdate=2020-03-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190522045137/https://www.forbes.com/sites/insertcoin/2015/03/14/cities-skylines-succeeds-where-eas-simcity-failed/ |archivedate=2019-05-22 }}</ref><ref name="RPS greatest PC" /><ref name="metro_uk_review" />。虽然如此，游戏仍被批評內容不足和設計缺陷<ref name="GSpot" /><ref name="kotaku review" />，例如缺少了天灾系统（天灾系统后来通过DLC发布引入）和随机事件，这些都是《模擬城市》拥有的內容<ref name="ign_review" />，另外，遊戲还缺少实用的指南來指引玩家<ref name="metro_uk_review">{{cite web |last=Hargreaves |first=Roger |title=Cities: Skylines review – the real SimCity |url=http://metro.co.uk/2015/03/19/cities-skylines-review-the-real-simcity-5110522/ |date=2015-03-19 |website=Metro |accessdate=2019-05-21 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190521030834/https://metro.co.uk/2015/03/19/cities-skylines-review-the-real-simcity-5110522/ |archivedate=2019-05-21 }}</ref>。

「小啾啾」是最受評論與玩家批評的遊戲功能。IGN的斯塔普萊頓抱怨小啾啾顯示的無聊內容<ref name="ign_review" />。Quarter to Three的汤姆·奇克（Tom Chick）在一篇「你永遠猜不到哪款新作有著遊戲史上最爛的角色」評論中表示小啾啾令他感到崩潰。遊戲已經有許多設計可以表現出汙染、噪音以及民生物資的缺少，不用多一個假推特發送一堆垃圾訊息提醒他該做什麼<ref>{{cite web |last=Chick |first=Tom |title=You’ll never guess which game has the new Worst Videogame Character of All Time |url=https://www.quartertothree.com/fp/2015/03/04/youll-never-guess-which-game-has-the-new-worst-videogame-character-of-all-time/ |date=2015-03-04 |website=Quarter to Three |accessdate=2020-10-03 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003024205/https://www.quartertothree.com/fp/2015/03/04/youll-never-guess-which-game-has-the-new-worst-videogame-character-of-all-time/ |archivedate=2020-10-03 }}</ref>。PC Invasion將可以屏蔽與刪除小啾啾的額外模組收錄在「城市：天际线必裝模組清單」<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.pcinvasion.com/essential-cities-skylines-mods-you-need/ |title=Essential Cities Skylines Mods You Need |date=2015-03-12 |work=PC Invasion |first=Paul |last=Younger |accessdate=2020-10-03 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003024541/https://www.pcinvasion.com/essential-cities-skylines-mods-you-need/ |archivedate=2020-10-03 }}</ref>。《PC Gamer》的里榮斯頓和God is a Geek的格雷格·希爾（Greg Hill）感激可以透過遊戲設置阻止小啾啾自动弹出或是選擇將其屏蔽<ref name="pcgamer review" /><ref name="GiaG_PC" />。玛丽娜·哈利凯宁在接受訪談表示：「這是遊戲最具爭議的功能，許多玩家恨死了這隻藍色小鳥」，身為當初建議加入小啾啾的提案者，哈利凯宁也笑說開發團隊應該不會想再聽到她發表意見<ref name="如何登頂" />。

隨著時間過去，《城市：天际线》陸續增加了許多內容，Kotaku的彭凱特在一年後重新遊玩《城市：天际线》，提到遊戲運行更加順暢，彭凱特喜歡DLC《冰天雪地》增加的內容，覺得天氣變化讓市民出現大量用電及大雪造成的道路壅塞是對玩家能力的考驗<ref>{{cite web |url=https://kotaku.com/12-months-later-hows-cities-skylines-going-1759776720 |title=12 Months Later, How's Cities: Skylines Going? |first=Luke |last=Plunkett |website=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |publisher={{link-en|Univision Communications}} |date=2016-02-18 |accessdate=2020-03-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327085432/https://kotaku.com/12-months-later-hows-cities-skylines-going-1759776720 |archivedate=2020-03-27 |deadurl=no |language=en }}</ref>。USgamer的邁克·威廉姆斯（Mike Williams）對《冰天雪地》13美金的售價有些意見，表示除了[[有軌電車|有軌電車]]，大多更新的內容都只是視覺方面，積雪特效也只能在本次新增的地圖使用，覺得因為增加有軌電車而花費13美金購買似乎顯得有些不合理<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.usgamer.net/articles/cities-skylines-snowfall-tests-the-limits-of-the-word-expansion |title=Cities Skylines Snowfall Tests the Limits of the Word "Expansion" |first=Mike |last=Williams |date=2016-02-16 |accessdate=2020-03-27 |language=en |deadurl=no |work=USgamer |publisher=Gamer Network |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327092034/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/cities-skylines-snowfall-tests-the-limits-of-the-word-expansion |archivedate=2020-03-27 }}</ref>。

GameSpot的布雷特·托德（Brett Todd）給予《大災難》、《公共運輸》、《工業》這三款DLC 7分、8分以及7分的評價，托德評論《大災難》擁有令人印象深刻的視覺表現，但份量上只是遊戲更新<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/cities-skylines-natural-disasters-review/1900-6416585/ |title=Cities: Skylines - Natural Disasters Review Build it up and tear it down. |first=Brett |last=Todd |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2016-12-06 |accessdate=2020-03-27 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327090824/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/cities-skylines-natural-disasters-review/1900-6416585/ |archivedate=2020-03-27 }}</ref>；《公共運輸》雖然有瑕疵，但解決了原本玩家處理[[大眾運輸|大眾運輸]]的困難<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/cities-skylines-mass-transit-review/1900-6416705/ |title=Cities: Skylines - Mass Transit Review Getting around just got easier. |first=Brett |last=Todd |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2017-06-22 |accessdate=2020-03-27 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327091147/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/cities-skylines-mass-transit-review/1900-6416705/ |archivedate=2020-03-27 }}</ref>；《工業》為城市增添了不少特色，但獎勵、挑戰的缺少都讓玩家覺得沒必要建立工業區<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/cities-skylines-industries-review-the-up-and-up/1900-6417029/ |title=Cities: Skylines - Industries Review - The Up And Up |first=Brett |last=Todd |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2018-11-06 |accessdate=2020-03-27 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327091031/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/cities-skylines-industries-review-the-up-and-up/1900-6417029/ |archivedate=2020-03-27 }}</ref>。

=== 移植版 ===
遊戲的主機移植分別於2017年和2018年推出，根據Metacritic的得分，Xbox One和PlayStation 4版本均獲得81分<ref name="MCXB1" /><ref name="MCPS4" />。評論讚賞遊戲不輸於電腦的畫面表現及完美契合的搖桿控制方式。

[[Windows_Central|Windows Central]]的編輯耶兹·柯登（Jez Corden）給予遊戲4.5顆星（滿分5顆星），認為遊戲令人上癮到會破壞玩家的人際關係與工作能力<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.windowscentral.com/cities-skylines-xbox-one-review |title=Cities: Skylines for Xbox One review — The best management game money can buy |first=Jez |last=Corden |work=[[Windows_Central|Windows Central]] |date=2017-04-21 |accessdate=2020-03-25 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325182506/https://www.windowscentral.com/cities-skylines-xbox-one-review |archivedate=2020-03-25 }}</ref>。Push Square的山姆·布魯克（Sam Brooke）提到遊戲在放大縮小畫面的時候會出現分辨率下降的問題，其他像是風力發電機的動態建築也會有卡頓的情形，但開發商透過簡單的[[控件|控件]]、數不清的細節和容易上手的玩法，讓本作兼具趣味和挑戰性<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pushsquare.com/reviews/ps4/cities_skylines_-_playstation_4_edition |title=Cities: Skylines - PlayStation 4 Edition Review (PS4) |first=Sam |last=Brooke |work=Push Square |date=2017-08-15 |accessdate=2020-03-25 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325183306/http://www.pushsquare.com/reviews/ps4/cities_skylines_-_playstation_4_edition |archivedate=2020-03-25 }}</ref>。

《CGMagazine》的兩位評論員科迪·奧姆（Cody Orme）、喬丹·比奧路迪（Jordan Biordi）分別給予8.5分、9分（滿分10分），讚賞遊戲對主機的支援程度，雖然鍵盤滑鼠仍是遊玩《城市：天际线》的最佳辦法，但搖桿也能做出相同的效果，只要動動按鈕就能輕易做出橫跨城鎮的道路<ref name="CGMXB1">{{cite web |url=https://www.cgmagonline.com/reviews/cities-skylines-xbox-one-edition-review/ |title=CITIES: SKYLINES – XBOX ONE EDITION REVIEW |first=Cody |last=Orme |work=CGMagazine |date=2017-04-21 |accessdate=2020-03-25 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325180752/https://www.cgmagonline.com/reviews/cities-skylines-xbox-one-edition-review/ |archivedate=2020-03-25 }}</ref><ref name="CGMPS4">{{cite web |url=https://www.cgmagonline.com/reviews/cities-skylines-ps4-review-skys-limit/ |title=CITIES: SKYLINES (PS4) REVIEW – SKY’S THE LIMIT |first=Jordan |last=Biordi |work=CGMagazine |date=2017-12-19 |accessdate=2020-03-25 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325180643/https://www.cgmagonline.com/reviews/cities-skylines-ps4-review-skys-limit/ |archivedate=2020-03-25 }}</ref>。

任天堂Switch版本的分數較低，在Metacritic上僅有67分<ref name="MCNS" />。媒體批評任天堂Switch上的糟糕畫面及不穩定的影格<ref name="MCNS" />。GameSpot的托德雖然很喜歡隨身攜帶的便利性，但隨著城市越建越大，小螢幕的缺陷逐漸明顯，光是縮放螢幕就耗費不少時間<ref name="GSpot" />。God is a Geek的馬蓋爾·瑪德納尼（Mikhail Madnani）給予6.5分（滿分10分），表示「以我遊玩近15個小時的感受，除非你能夠忍受醜陋畫面和差勁性能，否則根本不值得買」<ref name="GiaG_NS">{{cite web |url=https://www.godisageek.com/reviews/switch-report-review-31-cities-skylines-velocity-2x-subaracity/ |title=Switch Re:Port Review #31: Cities: Skylines, Velocity 2X, SubaraCity |first=Mikhail |last=Madnani |work=God is a Geek |date=2018-09-24 |accessdate=2020-03-20 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320205732/https://www.godisageek.com/reviews/switch-report-review-31-cities-skylines-velocity-2x-subaracity/ |archivedate=2020-03-20 }}</ref>。Destructoid的彼得·格洛戈夫斯基（Peter Glagowski）基於類似評價給予遊戲5分（滿分10分），談到除非玩家想要有隨身體驗城市建造遊戲的樂趣，不然別考慮任天堂Switch版本<ref name="Destructoid_NS" />。

=== 销售 ===
本作在24小时内共售出50万份，打破[[Paradox_Interactive|Paradox Interactive]]的歷年發行遊戲的紀錄成為最熱賣的作品<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2015/03/12/cities-skylines-sells-250000-in-first-24-hours |title=Cities: Skylines Sells 250,000 in First 24 Hours |first=Luke |last=Karmali |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |date=2015-03-12 |accessdate=2015-03-13 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20150313065108/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/03/12/cities-skylines-sells-250000-in-first-24-hours |archivedate=2015-03-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/03/17/cities-skylines-500k-sales-record/ |title=Cities: Skylines has doubled its day one sales |first=Brenna |last=Hillier |work=[[VG247|VG247]] |date=2015-03-17 |accessdate=2020-03-18 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318114629/https://www.vg247.com/2015/03/17/cities-skylines-500k-sales-record/ |archivedate=2020-03-18 }}</ref>，一个月内售出100万份<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/04/14/paradox-builds-up-1-million-cities-skylines-sales.aspx |title=Paradox Builds Up 1 Million Cities: Skylines Sales |first=Mike |last=Futter |work=[[GameInformer|GameInformer]] |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2015-04-14 |accessdate=2020-03-18 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318114841/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/04/14/paradox-builds-up-1-million-cities-skylines-sales.aspx |archivedate=2020-03-18 }}</ref>，一周年时已经卖出200万份<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vg247.com/2016/03/10/cities-skylines-has-sold-over-2-million-copies-76000-pieces-of-mod-content-created/ |title=Cities: Skylines has sold over 2M copies, 76,000 pieces of mod content created |work=[[VG247|VG247]] |date=2016-03-10 |accessdate=2020-03-18 |first=Stephany |last=Nunnely |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318114953/https://www.vg247.com/2016/03/10/cities-skylines-has-sold-over-2-million-copies-76000-pieces-of-mod-content-created/ |archivedate=2020-03-18 }}</ref>，两周年已卖出350万份<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.usgamer.net/articles/cities-skylines-turns-two-free-dlc-incoming |title=Cities: Skylines Turns Two, Free DLC Incoming |first=Nadia |last=Oxford |date=2017-03-10 |accessdate=2020-03-18 |work=[[US_Gamer|US Gamer]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318115157/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/cities-skylines-turns-two-free-dlc-incoming |archivedate=2020-03-18 }}</ref>。到了2019年，本作已累计售出600万份<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.3dmgame.com/news/201903/3757116.html |title=《城市：天际线》发售四周年 累计销量突破600万 |date=2019-03-09 |accessdate=2020-03-18 |author=druiber |work=[[3DM|3DM]] |language=zh-cn |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318115248/https://www.3dmgame.com/news/201903/3757116.html |archivedate=2020-03-18 }}</ref>。

