ate=2018-12-28 |accessdate=2017-10-05 |language=en |deadurl=no |website=[[Shacknews|Shacknews]] |publisher={{le|Gamerhub|Shacknews}} |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005043524/https://www.shacknews.com/article/92585/2015-game-of-the-year-9-cities-skylines |archivedate=2017-10-05 }}</ref>，而在一場由德國媒體PCGames舉辦，將近4100人參與的PC遊戲票選中，《城市：天际线》獲得第5名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pcgames.de/PC-Games-Brands-19921/News/Spiele-des-Jahres-Bestes-PC-Spiel-des-Jahres-2015-1180183/galerie/2375926/ |title=PC Games Spiele des Jahres: Bestes PC-Spiel des Jahres 2015 - ihr habt gewählt |first=Matthias |last=Dammes |date=2015-12-30 |accessdate=2020-03-22 |language=de |deadurl=no |work=PCGames |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322122212/https://www.pcgames.de/PC-Games-Brands-19921/News/Spiele-des-Jahres-Bestes-PC-Spiel-des-Jahres-2015-1180183/galerie/2375926/ |archivedate=2020-03-22 }}</ref>。USgamer收錄遊戲至「25款最佳Steam遊戲」名單<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.usgamer.net/articles/the-25-best-steam-games |title=The 25 Best Steam Games |author=USgamer Team |date=2020-02-03 |accessdate=2020-03-22 |language=en |deadurl=no |work=USgamer |publisher=Gamer Network |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322112109/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/the-25-best-steam-games |archivedate=2020-03-22 }}</ref>，《[[PC_Magazine|PC Magazine]]》將本作納入「9款你需要的Steam遊戲」當中<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pcmag.com/news/9-steam-games-your-pc-needs |title=9 Steam Games Your PC Needs |first=Gabriel |last=Zamora |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2020-03-21 |language=en |deadurl=no |publisher=[[PC_Magazine|PC Magazine]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321160738/https://www.pcmag.com/news/9-steam-games-your-pc-needs |archivedate=2020-03-21 }}</ref>，[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]提名遊戲為「2015年最佳PC獨佔遊戲」<ref>{{cite AV media |title=Best of 2015 Awards - Best PC Exclusive |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RicJublgxek |language=en |deadurl=no |date=2016-07-21 |accessdate=2020-03-22 |publisher=[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]] |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110152929/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RicJublgxek }}</ref>。{{le|Bleeding Cool}}評選《城市：天际线》為「年度最佳遊戲」第33名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bleedingcool.com/2015/12/28/bleeding-cools-game-of-the-year-selection-35-18/ |title=Bleeding Cool's Game Of The Year Selection: #35-#18 |first=Patrick |last=Dane |date=2015-12-28 |accessdate=2020-03-22 |language=en |deadurl=no |publisher={{le|Bleeding Cool}} |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322100006/https://www.bleedingcool.com/2015/12/28/bleeding-cools-game-of-the-year-selection-35-18/ |archivedate=2020-03-22 }}</ref>、[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]評選本作為第5名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.amazon.com/b?ie=UTF8&node=13576873011 |title=Amazon.com: Amazon Games Best of 2015: Video Games |accessdate=2015-12-25 |language=en |deadurl=yes |publisher=[[亞馬遜公司|Amazon]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225145936/http://www.amazon.com/b?ie=UTF8&node=13576873011 |archivedate=2015-12-25 }}</ref>。Game Debate將本作評為「年度管理」與「年度遊戲」第5名<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.game-debate.com/awards/2015/nominee/cities-skylines |title=Cities: Skylines Global Game Awards Nominee 2015 |work=Game Debate |accessdate=2020-03-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316134751/https://www.game-debate.com/awards/2015/nominee/cities-skylines |archivedate=2020-03-16 }}</ref>、並將「最佳擴展」頒發給DLC《夜生活》<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.game-debate.com/awards/2015/nominee/cities-skylines-after-dark |title=Cities: Skylines - After Dark Global Game Awards Nominee 2015 |work=Game Debate |accessdate=2020-03-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316135054/https://www.game-debate.com/awards/2015/nominee/cities-skylines-after-dark |archivedate=2020-03-16 }}</ref>。[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]評選本作為「2010年代最偉大的PC遊戲」之一和「2022年PC上最值得玩的20款經營遊戲」第4名，並稱其為城市遊戲的希望<ref name="RPS greatest PC">{{Cite web |url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2019/12/06/the-best-games-of-the-decade-on-pc/4/ |title=The greatest PC games of the 2010s |author=Rock, Paper, Shotgun |date=2019-12-06 |language=en |accessdate=2020-04-29 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200429032844/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2019/12/06/the-best-games-of-the-decade-on-pc/4/ |archivedate=2020-04-29 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/best-management-games |title=The 20 best management games on PC to play in 2022 |first=Graham |last=Smith |work=Rock, Paper, Shotgun |date=2022-01-01 |language=en |accessdate=2022-01-01 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220527225556/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/best-management-games |archivedate=2022-05-27 }}</ref>。

遊戲獎項方面，《城市：天际线》榮獲《GameInformer》的「最佳模擬遊戲」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2016/01/06/game-informer-best-of-2015-awards.aspx |title=Game Informer Best Of 2015 Awards |first=Jeff |last=Marchiafava |work=[[GameInformer|GameInformer]] |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2016-01-16 |accessdate=2020-04-02 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402041338/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2016/01/06/game-informer-best-of-2015-awards.aspx |archivedate=2020-04-02 }}</ref>、《PC Gamer》的「社群冠軍」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.pcgamer.com/community-champion-2015-cities-skylines/ |title=Community Champion 2015 — Cities: Skylines |author=PCGamer |work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]] |date=2015-12-26 |accessdate=2020-04-02 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402041520/https://www.pcgamer.com/community-champion-2015-cities-skylines/ |archivedate=2020-04-02 }}</ref>以及2015年Unity大賽「金立方獎」（Golden Cube）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mcvuk.com/development-news/unity-awards-2015-winners-revealed/ |title=Unity Awards 2015 winners revealed |author=MCV Staff |work=MCV |date=2015-09-24 |accessdate=2020-03-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316135753/https://www.mcvuk.com/development-news/unity-awards-2015-winners-revealed/ |archivedate=2020-03-16 }}</ref>。《城市：天际线》獲得兩次[[Steam大奖|Steam大奖]]提名，分別是2016年的「輕鬆愜意獎」及2017年的「-{zh-hant:世界已經夠殘酷了，大家和平相處吧;zh-hans:世界已冷酷至极，让我们携手前行}-」<ref>{{Cite web |title=Steam Awards names its first-ever winners |url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/12/31/14136362/steam-awards-winners-valve |accessdate=2019-02-16 |date=2016-12-31 |first=Owen S. |last=Good |work=[[Polygon|Polygon]] |publisher=[[Vox|Vox]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190216154646/https://www.polygon.com/2016/12/31/14136362/steam-awards-winners-valve |archivedate=2019-02-16 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=The 2017 Steam Awards winners are revealed |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/the-2017-steam-awards-winners-are-revealed/ |accessdate=2019-02-13 |date=2018-01-03 |first=Andy |last=Chalk |work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213183753/https://www.pcgamer.com/the-2017-steam-awards-winners-are-revealed/ |archivedate=2019-02-13 }}</ref>。在[[D.I.C.E.獎|第19屆D.I.C.E.獎]]上，《城市：天际线》獲得了「年度策略模擬遊戲」提名，但該獎項最後頒給了《暴雪英霸》<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-2016-dice-award-winners-updated/1100-6434830/ |title=The 2016 DICE Award Winners [UPDATED] |first=Chris |last=Pereira |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |date=2016-02-19 |accessdate=2020-03-16 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316132035/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-2016-dice-award-winners-updated/1100-6434830/ |archivedate=2020-03-16 }}</ref>。開發商Colossal Order憑藉《城市：天际线》獲得「芬蘭年度遊戲開發者」（{{lang|fi|Vuoden suomalainen pelinkehittäjä}}）的殊榮<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.tivi.fi/uutiset/cities-skylines-toi-vuoden-suomalaisen-pelinkehittajan-palkinnon/a352425f-c066-3917-a410-39e96bc42c10 |script-title=fi:Cities: Skylines toi vuoden suomalaisen pelinkehittäjän palkinnon |work={{Link-fi|Tivi}} |date=2015-10-30 |accessdate=2020-04-02 |language=fi |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402041833/https://www.tivi.fi/uutiset/cities-skylines-toi-vuoden-suomalaisen-pelinkehittajan-palkinnon/a352425f-c066-3917-a410-39e96bc42c10 |archivedate=2020-04-02 }}</ref>。

=== 现实影响 ===
Paradox Interactive总部所在地[[瑞典|瑞典]][[斯德哥尔摩|斯德哥尔摩]]在其新市鎮改造計畫中宣布成立了“我的邻居城市：天际线”（My Neighborhood Cities: Skyliness），試圖讓玩家、建築師、土木工程師和水土保持學者們一同在遊戲裡設計模擬新市鎮，以作為現實新市鎮未來的藍圖<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/av/39200838/video-game-cities-skylines-helps-plan-stockholm-development |title=Video game Cities Skylines helps plan Stockholm development |work=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=2017-03-08 |accessdate=2020-04-02 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402043326/https://www.bbc.com/news/av/39200838/video-game-cities-skylines-helps-plan-stockholm-development |archivedate=2020-04-02 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.pcgamesn.com/cities-skylines/stockholm-planners-to-use-cities-skylines |title=Stockholm to use Cities: Skylines to plan new real world district |first=Keith |last=Andrew |work={{link-en|PCGamesN}} |accessdate=2020-03-18 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318115524/https://www.pcgamesn.com/cities-skylines/stockholm-planners-to-use-cities-skylines |archivedate=2020-03-18 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.u-acg.com/archives/10779 |title=瑞典首都新市鎮，將由玩家和模擬城市遊戲景觀建造 |date=2016-08-27 |work=U-ACG |accessdate=2020-03-18 |language=zh-tw |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318115647/http://www.u-acg.com/archives/10779 |archivedate=2020-03-18 }}</ref>。其中在纪录片《My Urban Playground》提到，将会用本游戏来模拟一个公共交通运输系统<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/267926/Did_you_know_Stockholm_used_Cities_Skylines_for_urban_planning.php |title=Did you know Stockholm used Cities: Skylines for urban planning? |first=Christian |last=Nutt |date=2016-03-11 |accessdate=2020-03-18 |work=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318115923/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/267926/Did_you_know_Stockholm_used_Cities_Skylines_for_urban_planning.php |archivedate=2020-03-18 }}</ref>。

在[[韓國|韓國]]，由{{link-ko|韓國國土情報公社|한국국토정보공사}}舉辦的第二屆空間信息模擬比賽（{{lang|ko|제 2회 공간정보 시뮬레이션 경진대회}}）於2015年6月22日正式開放報名，選手們要透過《城市：天际线》完成三個比賽項目，獲勝選手將得到300萬韓元的獎勵<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thisisgame.com/webzine/news/rboard/1/?n=63242 |script-title=ko:시뮬레이션 게임 시티즈: 스카이라인, 공간정보 시뮬레이션 경진대회 참가 |work=이것이 게임이다 |date=2015-06-22 |accessdate=2020-04-02 |language=ko |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402144215/http://www.thisisgame.com/webzine/news/rboard/1/?n=63242 |archivedate=2020-04-02 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gov.kr/portal/cnstexhb/224 |script-title=ko:제 2회 공간정보 시뮬레이션(시티즈 스카이라인) 경진대회 |work=정부24 |date=2015-07-02 |accessdate=2020-04-02 |language=ko |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402144436/http://www.gov.kr/portal/cnstexhb/224 |archivedate=2020-04-02 }}</ref>。[[芬蘭|芬蘭]]的[[海門林納|海門林納]]政府也舉辦了類似活動，政府將待建設的區域做成遊戲地圖讓玩家發揮創意，並依據成品的創意、可行程度得頒發優勝者<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hameenlinna.fi/Palvelut/Kaavat-ja-rakentaminen/Kaavoitus/Cities-Skylines/ |script-title=fi:Cities: Skylines - Hämeenlinna, modaa kaupunki mieleiseksi |accessdate=2016-03-28 |work=[[海門林納|Hämeenlinna]] |language=fi |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328160048/https://www.hameenlinna.fi/Palvelut/Kaavat-ja-rakentaminen/Kaavoitus/Cities-Skylines/ |archivedate=2016-03-28 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rappler.com/technology/news/123474-finland-hameenlinna-cities-skylines-planning-contest |title=Finland city holds city planning contest using video game |first=Jaemi |last=de Guzman |date=2016-02-23 |accessdate=2020-04-02 |work=Rappler |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402123321/https://www.rappler.com/technology/news/123474-finland-hameenlinna-cities-skylines-planning-contest |archivedate=2020-04-02 }}</ref>。

